        <p>Advanced AcousticWerkes (AAW) is a Singapore-based IEM manufacturer founded in 2014 by Kevin Wang. AAW designs and builds custom and universal in-ear monitors across dynamic, balanced armature, electrostatic, planar, and isobaric platforms.</p>
        <p>A3H+ Lux runs the same three-driver hybrid architecture across universal and custom fit: NOVA open-vented armature, precision balanced armature, 10mm graphene woofer, 3-way crossover, and a four-position tuning switch.</p>
        <a class="bm-btn bm-btn--ghost" href="/pages/about-us">About AAW</a>
